\newlabel{fig:enron_comm}{{8}{10}{\textit {Top}: Louvain community sizes for the Enron email network (top 30 of 252 total), sorted by size. The rapid drop-off indicates a few dominant business-unit clusters and many small peripheral groups. \textit {Bottom}: Executive sub-network showing top senders for each VP/CEO. Node size is proportional to degree; edge thickness encodes email volume. \texttt {sally.beck@enron.com} (COO) is the largest hub}{figure.caption.9}{}}
